name: Cashier Sales Summary Report
query:
Select 
si.letter_head as "POS:Data:150",
si.owner as "Cashier:Data:150",
sum(sit.qty) as "Total Qty:Int:150",
sum(sit.net_amount) as "Total Sales Cash:Currency:300"
from `tabSales Invoice Item` sit join `tabSales Invoice` si on sit.parent=si.name where si.is_pos=1 and si.docstatus=1 and si.posting_date between %(from)s and %(to)s 
group by si.owner
